      "text": "**Examining User's Request**\n\nI've been analyzing the user's requirements. It's clear they're seeking a root cause analysis for a \"WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR\" blue screen, a fixability score, and reliability assessment. I understand they're not looking to stress test their components, just a decent assessment of their PC's temperature. The user wants the assessment using PowerShell or Python tools. I am now in Plan Mode, as I will be reading and analyzing the code. I have no edits to make just yet.",
