      "text": "**Researching iFixit Data**\n\nI'm currently trying to determine if iFixit offers reliability scores or fixability scores for PC components. My initial search didn't yield direct results. My next step is to refine my search terms to include specific PC component names, like \"CPU\" or \"motherboard,\" alongside \"iFixit reliability score\" and \"ifixit.\" I also plan to check for scripts on iFixit's website itself. I will then move on to PowerShell and Python scripts for system monitoring.",
