    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "Now I have a clear picture of the system:\n- **Laptop**: HP OMEN 15-ce0xx\n- **CPU**: Intel Core i5-7300HQ (4C/4T, 2.5GHz)\n- **Motherboard**: HP 838F\n- **RAM**: ~16GB\n- **GPU**: NVIDIA GTX 1050 + Intel HD 630\n\nThe WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR on this specific hardware... Let me check for common issues with this model and the i5-7300HQ.",
