      "type": "answer",
      "text": "The script revealed a **critical issue** I need to add to the analysis:\n\n---\n\n### CRITICAL FINDING: Disk Space\n\n**Both drives are at 99.3% capacity:**\n- **C:\\ (ADATA NVMe):** 470.6GB / 473.9GB — **99.3% FULL**\n- **D:\\ (HDD):** 924.8GB / 931.4GB — **99.3% FULL**\n\nThis is very likely a **major contributor** to your WHEA crashes. When the NVMe SSD is this full:\n- The SSD controller has no free NAND blocks for wear leveling → causes NVMe controller errors → WHEA\n- Windows can't write page files or crash dumps properly\n- The stornvme warnings in your event log directly correlate\n\n---\n\n### Updated Root Cause Analysis\n\n| Rank | Cause | Confidence | Change |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **1** | **NVMe SSD critically full (99.3%)** | **VERY HIGH (90%)** | **NEW — #1 cause** |\n| **2** | NVMe SSD firmware issues (ADATA SX6000NP) | **HIGH (75%)** | Same |\n| **3** | CPU thermal degradation (8 years old) | **MEDIUM (50%)** | Same |\n| **4** | Mixed RAM instability | **MEDIUM (45%)** | Same |\n| **5** | Outdated BIOS | **LOW-MEDIUM (35%)** | Same |\n\n### Can you improve PC temperature?\n\n**Yes, but prioritize these first:**\n\n| Action | Difficulty | Cost | Impact on WHEA |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **Free up 50GB+ on C:\\ drive** | Easy | Free | **HIGH** — immediate improvement |\n| **Update ADATA SSD firmware** | Easy | Free | HIGH |\n| **Update BIOS to latest** | Easy | Free | MEDIUM |\n| **Repaste CPU** | Moderate | ~$10 | MEDIUM-HIGH |\n| **Buy matched RAM kit** | Easy | ~$30-40 | MEDIUM |\n| **Improve laptop cooling (cooling pad)** | Easy | ~$15-30 | Helps temperature |\n\n### iFixit Summary\n\n| Aspect | Score | Verdict |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Fixability (NVMe)** | 9/10 | User-replaceable M.2 |\n| **Fixability (Thermal paste)** | 6/10 | Requires disassembly |\n| **Fixability (RAM)** | 8/10 | SO-DIMM slots |\n| **Fixability (CPU/GPU)** | 1/10 | Soldered — unfixable |\n| **Overall Reliability** | 3/10 | 8-year-old laptop, full drives, mixed RAM |\n| **Can you improve temps?** | **Yes** | Repaste + free space + cooling pad |\n| **Is it worth spending time?** | **Yes** | Free disk space alone may fix the crashes |",
